## 🚀 JavaScript Functionality Details

### Global Variables & State Management
- `cart[]` - Shopping cart items
- `bookings[]` - User bookings
- Local storage integration for data persistence

### Key Functions

#### Navigation & UI
- `initializeApp()` - Initialize application
- `scrollToSection()` - Smooth scroll to sections
- `updateMarquee()` - Marquee animation refresh

#### Product Management
- `filterProducts(category)` - Filter products by category
- `addToCart()` - Add items to shopping cart
- `removeFromCart()` - Remove cart items
- `updateCartDisplay()` - Update cart UI

#### Form Handling
- `submitInquiry()` - Process inquiry submissions
- `bookAppointment()` - Process appointment bookings
- `showFormMessage()` - Display form feedback

#### Bookings & Notifications
- `updateBookingsDisplay()` - Render bookings list
- `cancelBooking()` - Cancel existing bookings
- `showNotification()` - Show toast notifications

#### Local Storage
- `saveToLocalStorage()` - Save data to browser storage
- `loadFromLocalStorage()` - Load saved data on page load

#### Interactive Elements
- `showMemberDetails()` - Reveal member bio on hover
- `toggleEventDetails()` - Toggle event information
- `setMinimumAppointmentDate()` - Set date input constraints

